data.description: Very cute and well kept spacious 3 bed, 1.5 bath home located on a large lot, near shopping and dining and just minutes away from I-25! Includes small structure in back with electricity connected, great for workout room, office space, art studio, etc. 2 Carports for plenty of parking. Well maintained with many things updated, like sewer from street to house, vanity in bathroom & plumbing under sink. So much to offer.
